# Zeni - Final Technical Development Plan (Version 1.0)

## Vision

**Zeni** is a modern ride-hailing platform connecting passengers with nearby drivers through a fast, reliable, and secure mobile application.

The initial release focuses on delivering a polished Uber/Bolt-style experience. Future versions can expand into deliveries, courier services, and logistics, but those are intentionally excluded from Version 1.

