# Backend

For Version 1 we will use **Supabase**.

Supabase provides:

* Authentication
* PostgreSQL Database
* Realtime
* Storage
* Edge Functions
* Row Level Security (RLS)

No custom backend (NestJS) will be built initially. This keeps development faster and reduces operational complexity.

---

