# Version 1 Scope

**Included**

* Rider app
* Driver app
* Phone authentication
* Google Maps
* Live driver tracking
* Ride requests and matching
* Trip management
* Cash, Yoco, and MTN MoMo payments
* Ratings and reviews
* Push notifications
* Trip history
* Profile management

**Excluded**

* Admin dashboard
* Fleet management
* Driver referral system
* Passenger wallet
* Promo codes
* Ride scheduling
* Multi-stop trips
* Carpooling
* Food delivery
* Parcel delivery
* Corporate accounts

This scope keeps Version 1 focused on launching a dependable ride-hailing service. The architecture remains flexible enough to introduce a dedicated backend (such as NestJS) and an admin portal later without requiring a major redesign of the Flutter apps or the Supabase database.
